title: S. Con. Res. 2 (ENR) - Resolved by the Senate (the House of Representatives concurring), That effective January 5, 1993, the joint committee created by S. Con. Res. 102 of the One Hundred Second Congress, to make the necessary arrangements for the inauguration, is hereby continued with the same power and authority. The joint committee may accept gifts and donations of goods and services to carry out its responsibilities.
